### Create tenant
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/tenants
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "slug": "acme",
  "name": "Acme Corporation"
}

### Create another tenant
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/tenants
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "slug": "beta-soft",
  "name": "Beta Soft"
}

### Invalid tenant request
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/tenants
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "slug": "Acme Company",
  "name": ""
}

### Create tenant with custom correlation id
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/tenants
Content-Type: application/json
X-Correlation-Id: demo-correlation-tenant-create-001

{
  "slug": "gamma-tech",
  "name": "Gamma Tech"
}

### Invalid tenant request with custom correlation id
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/tenants
Content-Type: application/json
X-Correlation-Id: demo-correlation-validation-001

{
  "slug": "Gamma Tech",
  "name": ""
}

### List tenants
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/tenants

### Get tenant by slug
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/tenants/acme

### Get missing tenant
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/tenants/not-found-company

### List tenants with tenant context
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/tenants
X-Tenant-Slug: acme
X-Correlation-Id: demo-tenant-context-001